What We Are

	SSG is an asset management firm founded in 2009 and headquartered in Hong Kong. SSG is currently investing its third flagship fund, SSG Capital Partners III, L.P. The fund focuses on credit and special situations investments in Asia-Pacific.


What We Do

	SSG takes a hands-on value investing approach and strives to add significant value to its portfolio companies post-investment. The SSG principals have extensive credit and special situations investing experience throughout Asia. The firm benefits from the principals’ strong local expertise and network of business relationships.






