Our People
 







About SSG Capital Advisors, LLC



Title

    Dedicated Team  


Body

Meet Our Professionals
To successfully emerge from a challenging situation, each prospective client and referral source needs trustworthy, experienced professionals who are sharp negotiators and innovative thinkers willing to go the distance.
SSG has built a team of creative, pragmatic professionals with broad expertise in every type of transaction structure. Our entire team works for the client - highly experienced and ethical people who have the ability to quickly pursue parallel paths and deliver multiple alternatives.
A Partnership for Success
SSG’s Managing Directors work together for clients, are responsive to their unique situations and build value for the longer term while establishing trust and confidence in the short term. Their collective insight and expertise includes many industries and scenarios and fuels their ability to solve even the most complex challenges and situations, acting decisively to achieve the best possible outcomes.  Their success is time-proven and field-tested with over 300 transactions over the past decade.







J. Scott VictorManaging DirectorMark E. ChesenManaging DirectorRobert C. SmithManaging DirectorMatthew P. KarlsonManaging DirectorMichael S. GoodmanManaging DirectorTeresa C. KohlManaging Director


 



A Strong Team
Our team of investment banking professionals offers a depth of experience and leadership that delivers a great deal more for clients. Their specialized expertise and our collaborative culture enable them to respond to clients no matter the need: mergers and acquisitions, financial advisory, private placements, financial restructurings and valuations.







Michael J. GormanDirectorNeil Gupta, CFADirectorMatthew J. ArdenAssociateBrett E. KravittAnalystBrian A. McAuleyAnalyst
 
 



Strategic Alliances
SSG has developed strategic alliances with select partners to add value to our clients, deepen our expertise, and broaden our relationships. SSG clients are assured access to specialized knowledge and personal, responsive service.








The Solutions Team
With decades of shared history, the SSG founding partners are a seamless team with an exceptional focus that delivers results.  







J. Scott VictorManaging DirectorMark E. ChesenManaging DirectorRobert C. SmithManaging DirectorMatthew P. KarlsonManaging DirectorMichael S. GoodmanManaging Director


 
















